data.description: Lafayette, Louisiana's adorable three bedroom two bath home in a quiet neighborhood is something you don't want to miss out on. Home has been upgraded and remodeled recently featuring an open concept floor plan, beautiful huge island with lots of counter space and storage, large utility room, high ceilings with wooden beams, and many more upgrades. The huge backyard has a large wooden deck overlooking all the beautiful surroundings. This home even has an outside generator plug in with room to fit your large utility vehicles or a camper. Additional lot right beside is available and has frontage on the river. Schedule your showing today!
